reviews.text: Bad customer service n the worst! Its the same 2 lady when i came for the 2 days. One malay n one chinese. Esp the malay staff no smile , don look at pple ayes when answer. Rudeness! like not happy wprking there. Working in hospital people in pain so atleast show some empathy. But Nurses n doctor there are  super kind good. They did a great job on my wisdom tooth. Fast n painless.

Worst ever customer service who attend on patients needs. Ms Liza, u need to have basic customer service and have more empathy as you working in healthcare especially dental. Patients comes in with severe pain. Dental pain can cause pain all the way to brain. Waited from 850am, turned off at 1230 and ask to come back at 1.23 by  nurse Huda to reach at 1.45 is ridiculous. At 4.05 attended by doctor , x ray machine was already off n doctor doesnâ€™t even know how to operate one. So obvious all is preparing to pack up for the day. Need the nurse to come in n on the machine; and all she can do was to gv painkiller as the dental has no such speciality. Wasted my whole day in your clinic.

Came in 10 minutes early, waited for another 10 minutes.
The doctor checked my teeth, did an xray (the sound effect produced by the movement of the xray machine was pretty cool), after that the Dr reviewed my xray and explained it to me thoroughly.
Well the best of all is the scaling procedure, never had a dentist do for me so well. Enough said.
